Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.51,0:00:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.47,0:00:19.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger, the King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.39,0:00:21.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.27,0:00:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before his death
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.24,0:00:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drove people around the world to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.00,0:00:28.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure? If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.76,0:00:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it! I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.97,0:00:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men rushed onto the\NGrand Line in pursuit of romanticism!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.62,0:00:42.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly entered a Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.52,0:00:49.11,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We’re going to gather up all our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.11,0:00:54.95,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search of something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.95,0:00:56.38,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,ONE PIECE!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.08,0:01:06.77,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Compasses only cause delays
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.77,0:01:11.82,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Delirious with fever, I take the helm
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.46,0:01:24.11,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If the dusty treasure map has\Nbeen verified, it’s not a legend!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.72,0:01:30.43,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes to personal storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.43,0:01:35.55,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,simply ride aboard someone else’s biorhythm
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.55,0:01:37.99,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and pretend it isn’t there!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.36,0:01:44.83,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We’re going to gather up all our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.83,0:01:50.33,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search of something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.33,0:01:56.59,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,A coin in my pocket,\Nand you wanna be my friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.59,0:02:01.28,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We are, We are on the cruise!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.27,0:02:03.91,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We are!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.79,0:02:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.03,0:02:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.10,0:02:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger, the King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.84,0:02:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before his death
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.16,0:02:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drove people around the world to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.32,0:02:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure? If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.40,0:02:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it! I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.26,0:02:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men rushed onto the\NGrand Line in pursuit of romanticism!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.48,0:02:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly entered a Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.49,0:02:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tempest Kick! Lotus!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.04,0:03:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this! Song of Willow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.38,0:03:33.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the hell...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.76,0:03:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.67,0:03:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A voice...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.33,0:03:59.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.49,0:04:00.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.13,0:04:04.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you stopping, Nico Robin?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.13,0:04:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you listening, you woman\Nwhose very life is a crime?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.86,0:04:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Lucci! Drag her along!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.98,0:04:14.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grab her by her hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.40,0:04:19.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an order.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.01,0:04:22.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get moving, Nico Robin.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.20,0:04:32.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me... you still think that the\NStraw Hats are coming to your rescue?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.91,0:04:34.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.18,0:04:41.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you seriously still laying your\Nhopes on such weak-looking pirates?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.06,0:04:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only feeling you'll have is a sense of guilt.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.93,0:04:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll endlessly atone for your\Nsin of having lived until today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.47,0:04:56.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Nico Robin?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.13,0:05:21.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.09,0:05:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Wh-What was that?! I just heard a voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.04,0:05:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What was that voice?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.08,0:05:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? The space has opened up. Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.00,0:05:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There you are! Pigeon guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.48,0:06:09.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Resounding Bad News! Buster Call Invoked!"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.53,0:06:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm impressed... I'll say that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.75,0:06:21.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think that you've come\Nthis far... all by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.63,0:06:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't come by myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.92,0:06:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.26,0:06:29.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I could come this far by myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.38,0:06:31.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I wouldn't even wanna come by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.33,0:06:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike you guys, I'm not alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.94,0:06:41.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soon all my friends will come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.35,0:06:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tempest Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.27,0:07:04.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shave!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.61,0:07:07.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really starting to get the hang of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.94,0:07:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm starting to feel kinda sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.97,0:07:14.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a sailor. Don't say\Npathetic things like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.59,0:07:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm not a sailor. I'm a hero who\Nhails from the island of snipers...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.42,0:07:22.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...although my best friend\NUsopp-kun is a sailor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.96,0:07:26.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop talking nonsense. Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.94,0:07:29.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They dodged!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.72,0:07:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Th-That was close!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.42,0:07:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let your guard down!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.54,0:07:33.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.19,0:07:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And don't do things that are uncalled for!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.68,0:07:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.39,0:07:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?! What's that supposed\Nto mean?! How rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.20,0:07:41.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure are rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.76,0:07:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is no good... It's so\Nslippery that I can't stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.39,0:07:52.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even still...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.25,0:07:55.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...what a creepy power.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.87,0:07:59.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds like a bunch of sour grapes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.95,0:08:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since you don't come close to me\Nwhen it comes to strength and beauty...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.92,0:08:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I gave you the gift of silky skin
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.09,0:08:09.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so that you can at least come\Na bit closer to my beauty.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.76,0:08:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.91,0:08:16.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's very sweet of you. But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.76,0:08:19.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...there's a limit to how far you\Ncan go, right?! There's a limit!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.52,0:08:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there a limit to women's desire?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.52,0:08:25.52,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,500)}"Ticked!"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.64,0:08:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why don't you do it to yourself?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.57,0:08:34.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? I don't need it, because\NI'm already beautiful enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.78,0:08:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, what a bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.63,0:08:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.87,0:08:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.08,0:08:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just you wait. I'm about to get you back!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.09,0:08:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow, ow... That damn deer-gorilla!\NHow dare he mock me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.40,0:09:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But more importantly, the key! The key!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.98,0:09:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd better hurry to that secretary woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.38,0:09:13.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Deer-gorilla! Wait, you jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.26,0:09:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gather those who can still fight to\Nthe front of the Courthouse! Do it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.51,0:09:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't flinch! Capture the traitors!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.68,0:09:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You call us traitors?! Don't make me laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.56,0:09:51.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was you, the Navy, who's been\Nbetraying us for the past 50 years!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.31,0:09:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're pirates to start with!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.86,0:09:58.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with pirates\Nfighting against the Navy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.69,0:10:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Oimo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.60,0:10:07.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, Kashii!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.51,0:10:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll change our strategy and\Nbring them down individually!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.80,0:10:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attack unit! Concentrate\Nyour fire on Kashii's feet!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.09,0:10:23.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now! Charge!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.86,0:10:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We bow to nobody in human\Nwave attacks! Keep on going!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.58,0:10:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey! Kashii!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.65,0:10:41.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oimo is next! Prepare to fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.54,0:10:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The situation outside has changed?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.83,0:10:57.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The giants who changed sides\Nhave been trying hard for us,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.28,0:10:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I guess they are at the end of their rope.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.16,0:11:21.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Hey, hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.49,0:11:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! What a disaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.83,0:11:28.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think that a pirate would get this far...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.52,0:11:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, everyone, come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.52,0:11:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,CP9! What the hell are you all doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.50,0:11:38.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A pirate has gotten this far!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.05,0:11:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you listening?! Say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.27,0:11:50.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.92,0:11:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What you're holding is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.32,0:12:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whaaat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.78,0:12:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A... A... A golden transponder snail!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.55,0:12:33.14,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Navy"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.79,0:12:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The silver transponder snail\Nhas received a signal!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.95,0:12:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Buster Call has been requested!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.22,0:12:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Buster Call has been\Nrequested by Admiral Aokiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.95,0:12:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.24,0:12:33.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enies Lobby!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.14,0:12:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have five of the Vice Admirals\Nnear the destination respond!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.09,0:12:38.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Considering the distance,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.09,0:12:39.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's quicker to head\Nthere from headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.82,0:12:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How quick?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.45,0:12:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's possible to get there within 30 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.89,0:12:46.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Immediately have ten battleships\Nget ready to set sail,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.76,0:12:48.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and summon five Vice Admirals!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.72,0:12:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be swift!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.95,0:12:50.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.67,0:12:53.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Buster Call has been requested!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.58,0:12:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The destination is Enies Lobby!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.96,0:12:59.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have ten battleships get\Nready to set sail immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.86,0:13:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.21,0:13:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.44,0:13:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! Oh, crap! This one is\Nthe portable transponder snail.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.53,0:13:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What have I done? I wasn't careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.60,0:13:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of all things, I pressed the button\Non the golden transponder snail!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.56,0:13:15.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of all things...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.33,0:13:20.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I requested a Buster Call!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.96,0:13:37.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of all things...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.67,0:13:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I requested a Buster Call!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.94,0:13:49.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-Buster Call? D-Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.55,0:13:51.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this? Some internal communication?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.62,0:13:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How foolish! Cancel it right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.27,0:13:57.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Robin's voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.03,0:14:00.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or it'll be a disaster!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.48,0:14:02.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.72,0:14:05.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? "Cancel it"?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.59,0:14:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey. Who do you think you're talking to?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.03,0:14:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck is this broadcast?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.57,0:14:13.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.41,0:14:15.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.07,0:14:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Buster Call is great, isn't it?\NWhat's wrong with it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.57,0:14:30.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Chief Spandam's voice, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.59,0:14:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right... There's no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.01,0:14:43.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the chief of Cipher Pol No. 9.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.69,0:14:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to hand you over\Nto the Government smoothly,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.44,0:14:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I requested a Buster Call.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.85,0:14:51.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see no problem in that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.02,0:14:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what happens here,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.57,0:14:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we'll be able to annihilate\Nthe pirates for sure in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.88,0:15:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How foolish...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.48,0:15:05.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, didn't I?!\NThat won't be the end of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.30,0:15:09.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no humanity in that attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.59,0:15:14.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the Chief... but who's the woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.54,0:15:18.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The attack will completely burn\NEnies Lobby to the ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.09,0:15:21.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Buildings, people... the very island itself!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.09,0:15:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a nightmarish concentrated fire that\Nsacrifices everything to achieve its goal!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.23,0:15:35.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Buster Call!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.62,0:15:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know what happened in\NOhara twenty years ago. That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.74,0:16:03.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine. It means that this is\Nvery important to the Government.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.81,0:16:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that that idiot Cutty Flam has\Nburned the blueprints for Pluton...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.02,0:16:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...your existence is the only\Nclue to the ancient weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.43,0:16:30.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A military power that can turn this\Nwhole era upside down is at stake.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.36,0:16:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it improves our chances of killing\Nthose idiots trying to get you back,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.06,0:16:39.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even if it causes the death\Nof thousands of soldiers,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.52,0:16:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we can say that it's an unavoidable\Nsacrifice for our glorious future!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.03,0:16:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Above all things, my promotion is at stake, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.40,0:16:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! What's he saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.70,0:16:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's gonna sacrifice us?! You gotta be kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.84,0:16:58.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think of people's lives?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.77,0:17:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget that CP9 is the\NGovernment's secret organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.53,0:17:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we need 100 deaths in\Norder to save 1,000 lives,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.42,0:17:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we'll kill those 100 without\Nhesitation on the spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.48,0:17:22.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mercilessness is also\Na necessity for true justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.73,0:17:29.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, those incompetent soldiers\Nwho couldn't stop the invading pirates
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.86,0:17:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,are better off dead, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.64,0:17:40.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That portable transponder snail...\NThe line is connected.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.48,0:17:41.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.46,0:17:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahhh! Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.58,0:17:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did everyone hear what I just said?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.62,0:17:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-So... my name is Straw Hat Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.69,0:17:59.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.79,0:18:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone! Leave the island!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.59,0:18:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Buster Call has been\Nrequested on Enies Lobby!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.41,0:18:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you stay on the island, you won't survive!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.98,0:18:09.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't your concern!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.34,0:18:21.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--B...\N--Buster Call...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.87,0:18:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds like Buster Call has been requested.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.06,0:18:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is that man doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.60,0:18:32.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like there's some sort of danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.57,0:18:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me who's in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.55,0:18:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel sorry for you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.02,0:18:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even your hope is gone now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.49,0:18:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.45,0:18:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're used to situations like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.24,0:18:54.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pirate kid, what kind of\Ndestiny were you born with?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.35,0:18:59.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is getting even more interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.49,0:19:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Buster Call has been requested!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.70,0:19:06.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Battleships are coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.37,0:19:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get off of Enies Lobby!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.08,0:19:16.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Battleships are coming? Why are\Nthe Navy soldiers running away?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.21,0:19:18.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The woman said that the island\Nwill be burned to the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.64,0:19:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this is the Government's island!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.40,0:19:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How should I know why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.05,0:19:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey! If you guys're running away,\Nat least untie us first!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.94,0:19:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a Buster Call!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.50,0:19:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be dead if we stay here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.64,0:19:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring some ships to the front!\NGet ready to sail out!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.55,0:19:43.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Navy is coming to attack this place!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.63,0:19:49.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We got left behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.44,0:19:53.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What're we gonna do?!\NIsn't this dangerous?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.06,0:19:56.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been dangerous ever since\Nwe set foot in this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.35,0:19:59.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about Bro?! What's gonna\Nhappen to Big Bro Franky?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.94,0:20:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. If he doesn't come back here,\Nwe can't go back together!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.07,0:20:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Straw Hats, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.62,0:20:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what about us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.46,0:20:13.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What will... happen to all of us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.83,0:20:16.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't afford to waste time, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.59,0:20:21.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, we have to take them out quickly\Nand hurry to the Gates of Justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.69,0:20:22.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got an idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.78,0:20:25.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What? What idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.96,0:20:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A way to get the handcuffs off?\NOr a way to escape from here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.63,0:20:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are the renowned sword, Nose Storm.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.75,0:20:36.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is no time to give me a nice name!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.81,0:20:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper! What's taking so long?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.50,0:20:54.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you open your mouth\Nand say such stupid stuff?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.25,0:20:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the pirates really get away...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.23,0:21:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...how are you going to...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.07,0:21:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...take responsibility for it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.91,0:21:12.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.87,0:21:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where was Robin speaking from?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.35,0:21:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The other side of these doors.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.68,0:21:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let you pass. At least\Ngive me time to say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.51,0:22:15.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coo coo.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.50,0:22:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out of my way.\NRobin's behind those doors, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.07,0:22:22.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So she's there. So what?\NYou won't be able to see her...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.44,0:22:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...ever again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.69,0:22:28.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... I'll go there to see her!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.91,0:22:39.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be right there, Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.19,0:22:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?! My entire body is slippery!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.97,0:22:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. Now that Buster Call has\Nbeen requested, playtime is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.60,0:22:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tempest Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.15,0:22:57.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? A-A fake?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.23,0:22:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mirage Tempo. I'm right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.35,0:23:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.80,0:23:05.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Five Namis? Nami Strikes Back with Mirages!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.07,0:23:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
